---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
  class="mt-auto border-t border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-elevated)]"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-8 sm:px-6">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"
    >
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        Referencia rápida de atajos · Firefox, VSCode, Vim, Hyprland, Kitty, Zsh
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        © {year} · Arch Linux - Fravelz
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]/80">
      Super = tecla Windows. Los atajos pueden variar según tu configuración.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
